{"tid":1312790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想做而正確就做啦 仲咁緊張民意做乜","createTime":"2019-07-13T15:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T15:34:16.000Z","uid":1582,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18868f8748a1c778e6ce07c718267237facd8ec6","tid":1312790,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:05:20.000Z","msg":"14到依家咩人係對家一早分晒<br />\n今時今日有足足一個月時間<br />\n中立要歸邊一早歸晒啦<br />\n覺得啱既就去做啦<br />\n大家無限量支持呀<br />\n唔通你覺得民意喺班廢中嗰邊<br />\n佢地會出嚟擋我地咩？<br />\n唔好被人地幾隻字就打亂盤棋<br />\n見到大家被人打到仆街<br />\n然後被個民意/道德綁架而擋都唔擋<br />\n真係好心痛你地㗎 我地任何一個人都唔可以傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">判斷過覺得對事情有利而正確既就做啦<br />\n你地背後永遠有人支持你地呀<br />\n<br />\n聽日沙田見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34552a1bf9e11ac91790bf57787bd5d0b3d69321","tid":1312790,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1e2666b0ee5276ffa192d85a5e3f4a2a2d234e","tid":1312790,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:11:03.000Z","msg":"我地唔係打緊民意戰呀<br />\n要打民意戰要全部人認同先做<br />\n幾時先攞到全香港人認同？"},{"pid":"5ef31d6002a5dbf9722bf1a675e63c6ea6bb2383","tid":1312790,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"記住 我地先係真真正正企出嚟既民意<br />\n其他人講幾句冇成本既野唔應該成為我地既絆腳石"},{"pid":"d58c7805bbf4c0dacce3773831f9e4159a1f5760","tid":1312790,"uid":121324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"法新社記者好有武德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHK01記者好有武德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立法會議員好有武德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被迫跳橋少年寧死不抗品行高尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"